(29, 'B01ABKN71M', '\n\n\n\n\n\n<hr>\n<h1 class=\"a-size-base-plus a-text-bold\">\nAbout this item\n</h1>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"a-unordered-list a-vertical a-spacing-mini\">\n\n\n<li><span class=\"a-list-item\">\nFashionable Wood Grain Timer: Natural wood and dark wood that matches any decor. The wood grain texture adds color to your kitchen. This simple timer is also easy to see on the large screen and is easy to use\n\n</span></li>\n\n<li><span class=\"a-list-item\">\n(Highly Functional Timer) The dretec digital timer is useful when you want to keep track of the time, such as cooking and studying. Easy to set timer with 3 separate key buttons. It is easy to use by anyone, so it is also recommended for children\'s learning\n\n</span></li>\n\n<li><span class=\"a-list-item\">\n(Complete Timer Function) With a mount-up and countdown feature, you can manage your time. When the alarm is stopped, it will automatically return to the time you set it, so it comes with a repeat function that is useful when you want to stretch and reuse\n\n</span></li>\n\n<li><span class=\"a-list-item\">\n(Magnetic for Refrigerator) This stand can be used in 3 ways, with a strong magnet, and a hook hole. Easy to use as it can be placed in a location or hung according to your needs\n\n</span></li>\n\n<li><span class=\"a-list-item\">\nSpecifications: Size (W x D x H): Approx. 3.5 x 0.7 x 2.8 inches (90 x 19 x 70 mm); Weight: Approx. 2.2 oz (60 g); Uses 1 AAA battery; Maximum set time: 99 minutes 59 seconds\n\n</span></li>\n\n</ul>\n<!--  Loading EDP related metadata -->\n\n\n\n\n<span class=\"edp-feature-declaration\" data-edp-feature-name=\"featurebullets\" data-edp-asin=\"B01ABKN71M\" data-data-hash=\"364317170\" data-defects=\"[{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;defect-mismatch-info&quot;,&quot;value&quot;:&quot;Different from product&quot;},{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;defect-missing-information&quot;,&quot;value&quot;:&quot;Missing information&quot;},{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;defect-unessential-info&quot;,&quot;valu