(33, 'B07YBR9NSR', '\n\n\n\n\n\n<hr>\n<h1 class=\"a-size-base-plus a-text-bold\">\nAbout this item\n</h1>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"a-unordered-list a-vertical a-spacing-mini\">\n\n\n<li><span class=\"a-list-item\">\nDouble wall vacuum construction can be used for cold or hot liquid. The large wide mouth type allows you to smoothly fit ice made from household ice makers. Keeps cold (24 hours) and hot (12 hours). It can be used in various occasions such as office, outdoor, children\'s club activities and sports.\n\n</span></li>\n\n<li><span class=\"a-list-item\">\nA simple and timeless design that is great for everyday use. The clean form makes it easy to wash and the minimum parts you need to reduce the burden on household tasks.\n\n</span></li>\n\n<li><span class=\"a-list-item\">\nThe lid has a handle that allows you to easily take it with you when you\'re on a heavy load or on the go. You can take it without getting in the way when you pay at the convenience store or go to the dining room for lunch. By attaching a carabiner to the handle, you can connect it to your bag or belt or hang it.\n\n</span></li>\n\n<li><span class=\"a-list-item\">\nThis bottle has a simple structure called the body, lid and seal, making it a great helper for housewives who wash multiple water bottles of their family every day. It is very easy to wash because it is simple without any small parts.\n\n</span></li>\n\n<li><span class=\"a-list-item\">\nThe surface of the unit is powder coated to prevent slipping, so it is recommended for mountain climbing.\n\n</span></li>\n\n</ul>\n<!--  Loading EDP related metadata -->\n\n\n\n\n<span class=\"edp-feature-declaration\" data-edp-feature-name=\"featurebullets\" data-edp-asin=\"B07YBR9NSR\" data-data-hash=\"3034286356\" data-defects=\"[{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;defect-mismatch-info&quot;,&quot;value&quot;:&quot;Different from product&quot;},{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;defect-missing-information&quot;,&quot;value&quot;:&quot;Missing information&quot;},{&quot;id&quo