(61, 'B081CHNJ2D', '\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"a-unordered-list a-vertical a-spacing-mini\">\n\n\n<li><span class=\"a-list-item\">\nWide Range of Application Temperature &amp; Food Grade Material: Made of durable borosilicate glass, it can be applied to a wide range of temperatures from -400°F (-20°C to 400°C). Heat resistant glass reduces heat stretching and shrinkage by approximately 1/3 of other glass. So it is resistant to sudden temperature changes and can be placed in the microwave, dishwasher and oven. It also uses food grade silicone. Safe and hygienic preserved food, perfect for people who enjoy healthy and eco-friendly life.\n\n</span></li>\n\n<li><span class=\"a-list-item\">\n(Airtight and Leak Proof) Comes with a seal ring and a tight seal, so it won\'t leak even when you stand upside down. Not only that, it also has good storage performance, preventing moisture and taste loss and preventing oxidation and corrosion of foods. Reduces waste of food discarded and discarded, and can be placed in the fridge without staining other odors.\n\n</span></li>\n\n<li><span class=\"a-list-item\">\n(Excellent Design, Easy to Open) Features hidden air vents. Unique venting design allows the lid to be opened easily. Pay attention to detail to make the user experience better. Clear glass material allows you to easily identify food inside Microwave and oven safe for clear cooking It also has a better texture than baking material. It is smooth and easy to clean and leaves no aftertaste.\n\n</span></li>\n\n<li><span class=\"a-list-item\">\nVersatile and highly functional: There are a variety of uses, so you can choose from it freely. It can meet your different needs. You can fill fruits, store dry, or eat on your commute to work. Perfect for the whole family to work, travel, picnics, school and gym. Multiple sizes for your choice, meet your daily needs.\n\n</span></li>\n\n<li><span class=\"a-list-item\">\nNote: This product is available in three sizes: S 12.6 fl oz (370 ml)